data.text: In 2021, Rodney Billups became an Assistant Coach for the Portland Trail Blazers. Coach Billups was born in Denver, Colorado and played for and graduated from the University of Denver, where he received his degree in business management â€“ he was the Head Coach for five seasons at his alma mater. Billups is the younger brother of NBA All-Star and Trail Blazers Head Coach, Chauncey Billups. Coach Billups, and his wife, Natasha, have one child (Canden).
